As the legend says , he was a demon that rebelled against his own kind for the sake of the human world .
He defeated countless demons and their Emperor , Mundus , before sealing the gateway to the demon world .
Sport
Russian sports clubs named `` FC Spartak '' , of which FC Spartak Moscow is the most well-known , and Spartak sport society are named in honor of Spartacus .
The Spartakiad was a competition similar to the Olympic games for countries of the Soviet bloc . , This name was also used for pseudo-spoting event held every five years in Czechoslovakia .
It featured mass people formation moving in the choreographed way , very much resembling the opening ceremonial of Beijing Olympic games , only without expensive costumes end effects .
Swiss Professional Cyclist Fabian Cancellara has been given the nickname ` Spartacus '
