Love Chaser
`` Love Chaser '' is the 1986 single released by the Swedish hard rock band Europe .
It was taken from the album The Final Countdown , and was released only in Japan in the soundtrack album of the Japanese movie Pride One .
The track on the B-side of the single was `` Carrie `` .
Next year the single was reissued in Japan and was entitled `` Carrie '' with `` Carrie '' on the A-side .
The reissue had the same catalogue number -LRB- VIPX-1849 -RRB- as the first release .
The song was written by vocalist Joey Tempest in 1985 , and was first played on a tour in Sweden the same year , before it was recorded and included on the Final Countdown album in 1986 .
